com.xrtb.common

Class Configuration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xrtb.common.Configuration

  • public class Configuration
extends java.lang.Object
    The singleton class that makes up the Configuration object. A configuration is a JSON file that describes the campaigns and operational parameters needed by the bidding engine. All classes needing config data retrieve it here.
    Author:
    Ben M. Faul
